## Summary
This documentation explains Amplitude's Recommendations feature, which uses AutoML to help users achieve their goals by clustering similar users and identifying items most likely to increase conversion tendencies, with hourly retraining to incorporate new behavioral data. It's optimized for user-based personalization in e-commerce, marketplaces, and B2C subscription software, supporting three personalization types: assortment, next-best-action, and cross-sell.

